This 21' wide townhouse has a classic brick façade, is comprised of 5,400 sq ft, 4 bedrooms, 5 full baths and 2 half baths. The house has many unique architectural features, including dramatic double heights ceilings, 3 original fireplaces (one wood burning & two gas) and beautiful hardwood floors. Basalt stone tile flooring is found throughout the pool area, and the pool itself measures approximately 30' by 15' and 5,5' deep. There are also double height ceilings in the pool (27') and a chandelier, creating a grand impression.
